<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Blog Post Success</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header {
      background: #28a745;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-top-left-radius: 8px;
      border-top-right-radius: 8px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .message {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #28a745;
      background: #e9f7ef;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }

    .illustration {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  </style>
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/@dotlottie/player-component@2.7.12/dist/dotlottie-player.mjs" type="module"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      Blog Post Successfully Published!
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="illustration">
        <dotlottie-player src="https://lottie.host/2f761b93-e819-4a84-83e9-563b5e55a37b/GGAkeabkxm.lottie"
          background="transparent" speed="1" style="width: 300px; height: 300px" loop autoplay></dotlottie-player>
      </div>
      <p>Dear <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Congratulations! Your blog post has been successfully published on BlogSphere.</p>
      <p class="message">Your blog is now live for readers!</p>
      <p>Thank you for contributing to our community.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2025 BlogSphere. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>